9
00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:30.820
This is the AACR's oldest scientific achievement

10
00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:34.200
award, and it recognizes investigators who have made

11
00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:37.940
outstanding recent accomplishments in basic

12
00:00:37.980 --> 00:00:38.850
cancer research.

13
00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:43.500
Established in 1961 by the AACR and the

14
