100
00:05:55.780 --> 00:05:58.520
So, thank you again for all of this.

101
00:05:58.980 --> 00:06:02.710
So, I want to talk today about epigenetic mechanisms of cancer progression,

102
00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:03.520
and

103
00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:08.556
I want toThese are my affiliations, I'm mostly at

104
00:06:08.596 --> 00:06:12.456
Johns Hopkins. I have joint appointments at these other institutions Hopkins has

105
